{"tid":653465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又入波) 涉用「不求人」打9歲仔致周身傷　休班輔警被捕","createTime":"2018-05-04T17:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T23:55:14.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"00d20207801f3b3c54a4cf3fbeb5b3806869177a","tid":653465,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驚超聯</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又入波</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://usatthebiglead.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/neymar-goal-against-celtic-3.gif?w=500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusatthebiglead.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F12%2Fneymar-goal-against-celtic-3.gif%3Fw%3D500&h=7b4494ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉用「不求人」打9歲仔致周身傷　休班輔警被捕<br />\n<br />\n05月04日(五) 21:47<br />\n<br />\n大埔發生懷疑虐兒案，昨日(3日)5時許，大埔官立小學有教職員報警，指懷疑有學生曾遭虐待，警員到場後，發現一名9歲男童手腳多處有傷，傷痕有新有舊，將男童送院治理。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員經調查後認為事件有可疑，懷疑有人曾因瑣事於富善街一單位，以「不求人」襲擊男童，案件暫列對所看管兒童或少年人虐待或忽略，拘捕男童姓李父親(46歲)，疑與案有關，案件交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。李為休班輔警，晚上已獲准保釋候查，需於本月下旬向警方報到。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理並進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"d7903bf4fd49f40ea9da7e9ec7bdae870203779c","tid":653465,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"當職警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n休班輔警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n停職警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm